title: Lady Frankenstein German Widescreen Extended Cut

sources.title: Lady Frankenstein German Widescreen Extended Cut
sources.description: This Version of Lady Frankenstein is Widescreen, and extended... unfortunately it was also German Dubbed, and since there is a chance the Dub may be copyrighted I have not included it. If you would be willing to create subtitles for this movie from the German Dub, email me at Derkman96@gmail.com with a Subject of "Lady Frankenstein German Dub"
